Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:24.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:29.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}In springtime I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}Then skipping along，oh I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}I looked at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:45.51,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:51.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}I danced with the peanut butterflies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}Till time went and told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:57.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}to say hello but wave goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:23:02.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}A thousand sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:07.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}Oh put them in a jar
