Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:23.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}you say  and off I'll go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:26.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}Oh whistle round the world
